snippet.title: Frontier Paladin Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more about Frontier Paladin, play the demo, and Wishlist on Steam here - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2804970/Frontier_Paladin/

Frontier Paladin is a blend of action-adventure, RPG, and tower defense. We're launching on Steam soon!

'Hyperion' by Scott Buckley - released under CC-BY 4.0. www.scottbuckley.com.au
